results.title: Storm Warnings
results.description: As the FF battle the Captain Britain Corps, Johnny tries to figure out what's going on from Gatecrasher, then breaks into the Starlight Citadel and makes a deal with Opal Luna Saturnyne and Roma, allowing Franklin to stay with the FF.

results.title: A Day in the Life
results.description: Neal Conan and Manoli Wetherell, from NPR-TV, interview the FF; Johnny, Caledonia (a former slave Johnny rescued in the Core Continuum), Spider-Man, and Kraven the Hunter hunt for a creature in Four Freedoms Plaza, and find a puppy for Franklin.

results.title: Playing to the Camera Part 3: Legal Question
results.description: DD hires himself a lawyer in his suit brought by Griggs, but Griggs winds up painting him in a legal corner.

results.title: Playing to the Camera Part 4: Making Offers
results.description: DD traces Griggs' story of the night at the greenhouse back to his shrink; The shrink turns out to be the Matador who fesses up and then denies everything.

results.title: Playing to the Camera Part 5: Ruminations Over Manhattan
results.description: The trial of Daredevil begins with DD on the witness stand and Matt Murdock cross-examining him.

results.title: Playing to the Camera Part 6: Who Is That Masked Man?
results.description: A fake DD shows up at the trial letting Matt off the hook a little (but not before Matt fabricates evidence, perjures himself and basically does everything a lawyer isn't supposed to do) causing a mis-trial; DD tracks down the criminal mastermind responsible for the whole mess.

results.title: Underboss Part 1
results.description: Today: Kingpin's new man and a group of his lieutenants stab him Julius Caesar style and leave him for dead; One Week Ago: Matt and Foggy are leaving court when Nitro shows up and tries to blast Murdock.

results.title: [Underboss Part 2]
results.description: One Week Ago: A rookie cop tries to bust DD for assaulting a hood while he is trying to find out who sent Nitro after him; DD confronts the Kingpin about the situation and Fisk denies he had anything to do with it; Three Weeks Ago: Sammy Silke moves into town and starts making friends with the Kingpin's boys; Today: Ben Urich gets the call that the Kingpin is dead.

results.title: [Underboss Part 3]
results.description: Assassins are gunning for Daredevil and he can't figure out why.

results.title: [Underboss Part 4]
results.description: Today: Vanessa Fisk finds out her husband has been stabbed and in critical condition (and not killed as reports claim); Three Months Ago: Sammy joins the Kingpin's organization and asks for Murdock to be killed as a favor to his father; Kingpin forcefully declines; Two Days Ago: DD is told that the Kingpin has put the hit on him, and Wilson realizes that someone in his organization defied him to do it; Two Months Ago: Sammy regales the Kingpin's men with the story of a man who waited patiently until he got his shot and then took it.

results.title: Guardian Devil Part Three: Dystopia
results.description: Foggy is accused of murdering the client he took to bed, and his mother cuts him loose to protect the law-firm; Macabes lets Karen know that it is the little child who is messing up everyone's lives; DD is abducted and confronted by an angel looking for the missing child.

results.title: [Underboss Part 5]
results.description: Today: Ben and Matt have a heart to heart about the killing of the Kingpin; Two Months Ago: Sammy convinces Richard to help him revolt against the Kingpin; One Month Ago: Sammy convinces the rest of Kingpin's goons to join the plot; Today: Kingpin is airlifted out of New York, but Vanessa stays behind to take care of family business.

results.title: [Underboss Part 6]
results.description: Vanessa starts killing the men who turned on her husband, starting with her own son; Sammy runs to the feds and reveals that Matt Murdock is Daredevil.
